</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>

<h2>iHousing's Automated Solution</h2>

<p>Managing tax filings is a headache. iHousing simplifies this:</p>
<ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6">
    <li><strong>Automated Collection:</strong> We configure the platforms to collect taxes automatically where possible.</li>
    <li><strong>Monthly Reporting:</strong> We generate a tax report for you.</li>
    <li><strong>Filing Assistance:</strong> We guide you on how to submit payments to the local council.</li>
</ul>

